name: Commodore Format Power Pack 33
description:
Commodore Format Power Pack 33 is a collection of games, demos and utilities found attached to the cover of the monthly Commodore 64 magazine Commodore Format in Cassette form. Issue 33 (June 1993) contains:
  • Water Polo (Full Game)
  • Corya (Part 2) (Full Game)
  • ATA: Game released on Public Domain (Full Game)
  • Snack Man: Game released on Public Domain (Full Game)
  • Sprite Demo: A game to be played as part of a feature found on p23 called 'Do The Sprite Thing' (Utility)
